==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Connector
<hw>Con*nect"or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, connects</def>; as: <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A flexible tube for
connecting the ends of glass tubes in pneumatic experiments.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>A device for holding two parts of an electrical
conductor in contact.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Conner</ent>⟦br⟧
